            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<hr>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_rA76" id="6-opensourcemdx">6. opensource.mdx<a href="https://monoblog.cc.cd/blog/2026/February/opensource#6-opensourcemdx" class="hash-link" aria-label="6. opensource.mdx的直接链接" title="6. opensource.mdx的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<div class="language-mdx codeBlockContainer_Z2cf theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#bfc7d5;--prism-background-color:#292d3e"><div class="codeBlockContent_GmT7"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-mdx codeBlock_WcJL thin-scrollbar" style="color:#bfc7d5;background-color:#292d3e"><code class="codeBlockLines_Oe7t"><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">---</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">title: 我的开源项目：MonoBlog 个人博客</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">date: 2025-06-03</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">slug: opensource</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">tags: [开源, Docusaurus, 博客系统]</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">excerpt: 介绍基于 Docusaurus + Supabase 搭建的个人博客开源项目，包含功能、技术栈与使用说明。</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">---</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain"># 我的开源项目：MonoBlog 个人博客</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">本文介绍我搭建的个人博客开源项目，基于 Docusaurus 静态站点框架 + Supabase 后端服务。</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">## 一、项目功能</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">本博客完整实现以下功能：</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">- 静态页面部署，支持 GitHub Pages 免费托管</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">- 邮箱 / GitHub 双渠道账号登录</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">- 侧边栏实时评论区</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">- 在线用户数量、最新注册用户实时统计</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">- 全站移动端自适应布局</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">- 文章分类、标签、导航跳转</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">## 二、技术栈</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">- **前端框架**：Docusaurus（基于 React）</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">- **样式/布局**：原生 CSS + Flex 弹性布局</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">- **后端服务**：Supabase（BaaS 云服务，提供认证、数据库）</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">- **部署平台**：GitHub Pages</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">## 三、开源地址</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">项目已开源，欢迎 Star、Fork、提 Issue 交流：</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">&gt; 地址：https://github.com/ye2f4/pblot</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">## 四、使用建议</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">1. 克隆代码到本地，安装依赖后即可本地运行调试；</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">2. 自行配置 Supabase 密钥、站点域名、路由信息；</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">3. 支持自定义样式、导航、文章内容，可二次开发。</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">## 总结</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">该项目适合想搭建个人技术博客、学习 Docusaurus + Supabase 组合方案的开发者，欢迎大家一起交流学习。</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></div></code></pre></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
        </item>
