            <title><![CDATA[2026/February/tools]]></title>
            <link>https://monoblog.cc.cd/blog/2026/February/tools</link>
            <guid>https://monoblog.cc.cd/blog/2026/February/tools</guid>
            <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 17:14:11 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[---]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<hr>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_rA76" id="4-toolsmdx">4. tools.mdx<a href="https://monoblog.cc.cd/blog/2026/February/tools#4-toolsmdx" class="hash-link" aria-label="4. tools.mdx的直接链接" title="4. tools.mdx的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<div class="language-mdx codeBlockContainer_Z2cf theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#bfc7d5;--prism-background-color:#292d3e"><div class="codeBlockContent_GmT7"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-mdx codeBlock_WcJL thin-scrollbar" style="color:#bfc7d5;background-color:#292d3e"><code class="codeBlockLines_Oe7t"><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">---</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">title: 提升开发效率的 VSCode 常用插件</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">date: 2025-06-05</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">slug: tools</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">tags: [开发工具, VSCode, 效率工具]</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">excerpt: 分享日常开发高频使用的 VSCode 插件，覆盖代码格式化、语法检查、Git 管理等场景。</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">---</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain"># 提升开发效率的 VSCode 常用插件</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">VSCode 是主流代码编辑器，搭配插件可以极大提升开发效率，下面分享我日常必备的插件。</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">## 1. Prettier</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">代码自动格式化工具，支持 JS/CSS/MDX 等几乎所有文件，保存文件即可自动统一代码风格。</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">## 2. ESLint</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">代码语法检查，排查语法错误、不规范写法，团队协作必备。</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">## 3. GitLens</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">Git 增强插件，在行内直接查看代码提交记录、作者、时间，追溯代码变更非常方便。</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">## 4. Auto Rename Tag</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">自动同步修改 HTML/JSX 标签，修改开始标签时，闭合标签自动同步修改。</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">## 5. Path Intellisense</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">文件路径自动补全，导入模块、引用资源时自动提示路径，减少手动输入错误。</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">## 6. REST Client</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">在编辑器内直接测试 HTTP 接口，无需额外安装 Postman。</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">## 7. Markdown All in One</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">Markdown/MDX 增强插件，优化文档编写、预览、表格/列表快捷操作。</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">## 总结</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">以上插件覆盖了编码、格式化、版本管理、接口测试等全流程，推荐前端/全栈开发者安装使用。</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></div></code></pre></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
        </item>
