<p>使用官方脚手架快速创建 React 项目：</p>
<div class="language-bash codeBlockContainer_Z2cf theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#bfc7d5;--prism-background-color:#292d3e"><div class="codeBlockContent_GmT7"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-bash codeBlock_WcJL thin-scrollbar" style="color:#bfc7d5;background-color:#292d3e"><code class="codeBlockLines_Oe7t"><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token comment" style="color:rgb(105, 112, 152);font-style:italic"># 安装脚手架</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token function" style="color:rgb(130, 170, 255)">npm</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token function" style="color:rgb(130, 170, 255)">install</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token parameter variable" style="color:rgb(191, 199, 213)">-g</span><span class="token plain"> create-react-app</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token comment" style="color:rgb(105, 112, 152);font-style:italic"># 创建项目</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">create-react-app my-react-demo</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token comment" style="color:rgb(105, 112, 152);font-style:italic"># 启动项目</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token builtin class-name" style="color:rgb(255, 203, 107)">cd</span><span class="token plain"> my-react-demo</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token function" style="color:rgb(130, 170, 255)">npm</span><span class="token plain"> start</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></div></code></pre></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
