            <description><![CDATA[Minecraft 拥有庞大的模组生态，本文基于 Forge 加载器，讲解模组开发入门流程。]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Minecraft 拥有庞大的模组生态，本文基于 Forge 加载器，讲解模组开发入门流程。</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_rA76" id="一环境准备">一、环境准备<a href="https://monoblog.cc.cd/blog/minecraft#%E4%B8%80%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87" class="hash-link" aria-label="一、环境准备的直接链接" title="一、环境准备的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<ol>
<li class="">安装 <strong>Java Development Kit (JDK)</strong>（对应游戏版本要求）</li>
<li class="">下载对应游戏版本的 <strong>Forge MDK</strong>（模组开发包）</li>
<li class="">使用 IDEA / Eclipse 导入开发工程</li>
</ol>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_rA76" id="二模组主类">二、模组主类<a href="https://monoblog.cc.cd/blog/minecraft#%E4%BA%8C%E6%A8%A1%E7%BB%84%E4%B8%BB%E7%B1%BB" class="hash-link" aria-label="二、模组主类的直接链接" title="二、模组主类的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>模组入口主类，负责初始化、注册各类游戏内容：</p>
<div class="language-java codeBlockContainer_Z2cf theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#bfc7d5;--prism-background-color:#292d3e"><div class="codeBlockContent_GmT7"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-java codeBlock_WcJL thin-scrollbar" style="color:#bfc7d5;background-color:#292d3e"><code class="codeBlockLines_Oe7t"><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">import net.minecraftforge.fml.common.Mod;</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">@Mod("demo_mod")</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">public class DemoMod {</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">    public static final String MOD_ID = "demo_mod";</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">    public DemoMod() {</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">        // 执行注册、初始化逻辑</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">    }</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain">}</span><br></div><div class="token-line" style="color:#bfc7d5"><span class="token plain" style="display:inline-block"></span><br></div></code></pre></div></div>]]></content:encoded>
